her companies in japan offer a baby bonus for employees who have children the payments range from us for a first child to us for a fifth child see alsoedit companies portal list of mobile network operators of the asia pacific region list of telephone operating companies notesedit  a b c d e investor relations financial results highlights wwwsoftbankjp softbank group corp retrieved  august    about softbank corporate data wwwsoftbankjp softbank group corp retrieved  august    additional purchases of sprint corporation shares softbank august   retrieved august     changes of corporate names softbank group  retrieved    jp wwwbloombergcom bloomberg lp retrieved  march    forbes global  forbescom forbes retrieved  august    historical market caps of the largest japanese companies retrieved  april    httpwwwpwccomgxenauditservicescapitalmarketpublicationsassetsdocumentpwctoppdf  ボーダフォン、メールのドメインも「ソフトバンク」へ──から in japanese itmedia mobile  retrieved    ：ケータイ「ないしょにしてね」 in japanese sports nippon archived from the original on  retrieved    softbank profit soars buys stake in ustream japan today february     head lines jp yahoo dead link  santos alexis  softbank to acquire competitor eaccess expand lte network by  percent engadget retrieved    softbank to buy  percent stake in sprint sources cnbc retrieved october     soni phalguni the latest word in telecom market realist market realist inc retrieved april     olacabs raises  million from japans softbank corp enters b club the times of india october     startup housingcom valued at rs  crore after softbank acquires  stake for  million the times of india november     jt quigley may   postacquistion sic dramafever has more muscle to spread asian entertainment to the west tech in asia retrieved may     martin alexander may   softbank ceo taps a future successor in nikesh arora the wall street journal the wall street journal retrieved  may    changes of corporate names of softbank corp and subsidiary  press releases  news  about us